::Aerotaur::
      "Fascinating.  I am Aerotaur.  I came to answer the call they sent out."  He gestures to Shadow Cat and Snow Tech.  "I know that you don't know me but you might remember Trinity.  I have been caring for her since she fell off of your back at the battle.  We have our own little group now.  It's growing.  I would like you to come back and speak with her.  Unfotunately I don't know where they are right now.  Windlord should be here by now."  Just then he recieves Windlord's message.  "This is Aerotaur.  Is there a problem Windlord?"
